523
00:37:35,920 --> 00:37:40,300
<i>I'll fight against all injustices in the whole world.</i>

524
00:37:40,300 --> 00:37:45,220
<i>And I won't let go of anyone who's in trouble.</i>

525
00:37:48,480 --> 00:37:52,240
Of course, we can't just sit back and do nothing about Lingshuang Pavilion.

526
00:37:52,240 --> 00:37:55,320
